{"tid":1305781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［靚圖請傳俾老野睇］今日新彊，會是明日香港嗎？","createTime":"2019-07-11T02:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:07:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6e630f7e4d63ad38ac235b9c78ea616a0012cf","tid":1305781,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/105225_3d053a7ec99011597631741deea45ddc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F105225_3d053a7ec99011597631741deea45ddc.png&h=82760190&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/105226_572233531a6a54f89b32aae1297f804f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F105226_572233531a6a54f89b32aae1297f804f.png&h=774fcb74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/105228_42672a2e4b397f5ecedcf40be3ed9af6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F105228_42672a2e4b397f5ecedcf40be3ed9af6.png&h=f64940ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/105229_7e05bb9b0715181f92758092bee8dac2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F105229_7e05bb9b0715181f92758092bee8dac2.png&h=83ca86d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/105230_53a882e9972ae8f99bdfbcd265aacaa3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F105230_53a882e9972ae8f99bdfbcd265aacaa3.png&h=1f914e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10 年前的 7 月 5 日，新疆上千名維吾爾族人為追究兩名同族工人遭打死事件，上街遊行演變成大規模騷亂，自此中國管治新疆漸轉高壓，政府對人民處處提防，佈下天羅地網監控人民。人們連買白砂糖也要出示身份證，而且每人只能買 1 公斤，原因是官方指白砂糖可以用來製作炸藥。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n在香港，有記者在採訪衝突現場期間，被警方要求搜袋，遭質問所攜帶的水樽是否用作襲警；「三罷」前夕，大量市民在地鐵站無故被警察截查，需靠牆一字排開等候搜身；有警察在衝突清場後截停小巴，搜查半小時&hellip;&hellip;此情此景，也許不必遙想歷史上某極權，在同一年代，新疆的監控世界也是現成的範例。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n新疆的監控達至前所未見的嚴重，尤其針對維吾爾族人。警方在街上的檢查點超過 7,300 個，可隨意截查市民，並查看手機內容。國際組織「人權觀察」揭發，新疆警方使用一個名為「一體化聯合作戰平台」的手機應用程式，透過偵測維族人的手機、汽車和身份證，並收集其行蹤、藏書數量、禱告習慣、銀行戶口等資料，整合「危害政權」的人民黑名單，予公安追查。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n成千上萬的新疆人被送到「再教育營」，每天唱頌讚黨國的歌曲、念口號、學習漢語和中國歷史，灌輸「愛國意識」；據英國 BBC 報道，就算是穆斯林的子女，也要被送進寄宿學校，集中再教育。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n就連回家，居民都需要先在社區門口排隊掃瞄身分證或人臉。有烏魯木齊的居民無奈地說：「回家還要刷臉、刷身分證，這哪是回家，這就跟進監獄一樣！」﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n對香港人說，監獄的氣息可能只會愈來愈近。早前有在新疆專門從事人臉識別保安系統的公司透露，曾為港珠澳大橋香港口岸提供人臉相關的設備及軟件。事實上，香港入境處 2017 年也已於機場引入容貌識別技術，核實部分訪港旅客身份&hellip;&hellip;這些是便利，還是監控之始？﻿<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156467569265208&amp;id=81698200207&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156467569265208%26id%3D81698200207%26__tn__%3D%252As%252As-R&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=325e8140\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156467569265208&amp;id=81698200207&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R</a>"},{"pid":"afce0ca13390607a22f1373f39a766e08b935be8","tid":1305781,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:55:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06f80bdba62920ac74a3e5a52af611acfe772123","tid":1305781,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58f9f961af6ea267feb2d0f2500b7e5abee441d9","tid":1305781,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df48fcbe20b997432ed3fef2567e5c2a844eae3b","tid":1305781,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"癡撚線"},{"pid":"4fe421762a7e36a3db069b3e826de72362ef4438","tid":1305781,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0